E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Rachel Zoe: Things get wild at Los Angeles Zoo with a shoot involving a jaguar. And things get wilder when one model reads another's diary... (S16 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch Strictly Come Dancing, Our Dementia Choir Sings Again with Vicky McClure, My Possessed Pet, This Morning and The Ex-Wife. (S20 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box this time: I Can See Your Voice, Emmerdale, Strictly, Unbreakable, The Ex-Wife, Bargain Hunt, and the News on Jeremy Hunt becoming 2022's fourth Chancellor. (S20 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Finding the right man has been a tall order for 6' 3" Nikki; how does 6' 4" Ross measure up? And is there a spark when laboratory engineer Daniel meets lingerie designer Lauren? (S9 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bakersfield Expedition: The guys get all dressed up for a photo opportunity at a Star Trek location but end up stranded in the desert. (S6 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Cooper/Kripke Inversion: Sheldon is forced to work on the same project as his nemesis, Barry Kripke. Howard and Raj spend a fortune on personalised action figures. (S6 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch Strictly Come Dancing, Our Dementia Choir Sings Again with Vicky McClure, My Possessed Pet, This Morning and The Ex-Wife. (S20 Ep6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Treehouse of Horror IV: Homer sells his soul to the devil for a donut, no one believes Bart can see an evil goblin, and Mr Burns invites the Simpsons for tea at a spooky castle. (S5 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Sneeze, Detention, and Sissy Spacek: Sheldon's germophobia lands him in detention when flu season hits town and he takes extreme measures to stay healthy. (S1 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Potato Salad, a Broomstick, and Dad's Whiskey: When Mary takes a job as church secretary, she finds herself becoming a marriage counsellor to Pastor Jeff. (S1 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Stuck in a Moment: Haley wants to give the family a Christmas gift they'll never forget - if she can find the perfect time. Claire is mad when Phil borrows the Christmas tree. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mini Murray: Barry wants money to buy an expensive new pair of basketball shoes, so Murray hires him to work at his furniture shop so he can earn it. (S1 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Why're You Hitting Yourself?: Determined to get Pops to settle down, Beverly plays matchmaker for her father and pairs him up with a woman called Sophia. (S1 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Big One: The Butlers and Johnsons are rattled after an earthquake, and Calvin and Tina move in with Malcolm and Marty while their home gets fixed. (S4 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Stakeout: When there's a break-in at Calvin's business, he teams up with Dave for a stakeout to catch the culprit. (S4 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Neighborhood
E4Plus1.uk.description: Welcome to the Big Little Leagues: Calvin and Malcolm butt heads on coaching styles as Malcolm's little league team approaches its first game of the season. (S4 Ep14)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Warren tries to support Mercedes, but his scorned ex-girlfriend is never far away. Guilt consumes one resident. Frankie opens up about her past. And a new mum continues to struggle.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sienna, Dodger and the McQueens help new mum Cleo as she finally gets the support she needs. The Osbornes get to know Frankie's new beau. Gemma tries to build bridges with Mercedes.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring sheep.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bella Luna: Gordon visits Italian family restaurant Bella Luna, which is struggling with an inexperienced chef and an owner who won't acknowledge the eatery's flaws. (S7 Ep8) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Revisit: Gordon Ramsay revisits three restaurants he's helped: La Galleria 33 in Boston; The Olde Hitching Post in Massachusetts; and the Prohibition Grille in Washington. (S7 Ep9) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fabulous Faker Boy: Bart doesn't want to go to piano lessons, until he meets his beautiful teacher... Homer loses the last two hairs on his head. (S24 Ep20/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Saga of Carl: Homer, Moe, Lenny and Carl win the lottery, but Carl runs off to Iceland with the winnings. (S24 Ep21/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Line Substitution Solution: Sheldon pays Stuart to spend the afternoon shopping with Amy so that he can queue up to see a special film screening instead. (S9 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Convergence Convergence: Conflict arises when Leonard's recently divorced parents and Sheldon's devoutly religious mother are all in town at the same time. (S9 Ep24)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Long Honeymoon: Summer has been blissful in the Dunphy house with Alex away and the family getting along. But when Alex returns home, the atmosphere immediately changes. (S6 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Do Not Push: A campus tour becomes an emotionally and psychologically charged experience for the Dunphys. (S6 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Electric Can Opener Fluctuation: Leonard's attempts to woo Penny are constantly thwarted. Sheldon heads to Texas after learning his friends meddled with his expedition data. (S3 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Jiminy Conjecture: Leonard and Penny feel awkward around each other after their romantic liaison, while Sheldon and Howard take bets to determine a species of cricket. (S3 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Gothowitz Deviation: Sheldon tries to modify Penny's behaviour, and rewards her with chocolate when she does what he wants, while Howard and Raj go to a goth nightclub. (S3 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Pirate Solution: Raj must find a job or he'll be sent back to India, so he accepts an offer of work from Sheldon. Leonard and Penny try to get some time for themselves. (S3 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dolomite, Apple Slices, and a Mystery Woman: Sheldon makes a new friend, while Mary and George disagree on how to handle Sheldon's blossoming social life. (S1 Ep15/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Killer Asteroids, Oklahoma, and a Frizzy Hair Machine: A disappointing lack of success in a science fair competition sends Sheldon's life in a new direction. (S1 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Girl on the Bus: Lisa discovers the ideal family - and lies about her own. (S30 Ep12/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: I'm Dancing as Fat as I Can: Homer's broken promise infuriates Marge, so he studies ballroom dancing to try to win her back. (S30 Ep13/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Plimpton Stimulation: When Sheldon meets a famous physicist online, he invites her over to the apartment, where she spends her time flirting with Leonard. (S3 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Staircase Implementation: Leonard tells Penny about how he and Sheldon became friends, and the origins of the roommate agreement. (S3 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Lunar Excitation: Raj registers Sheldon for online dating and finds the perfect match: the female version of Sheldon. Penny seduces Leonard while she's drunk. (S3 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Robotic Manipulation: Penny tags along to Sheldon's first date with a woman he's been texting for months. Howard finds a new use for a robotic arm. (S4 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Boy-Scoutz 'n the Hood: During an all-syrup Squishee bender, Bart joins the junior campers, and ends up taking the embarrassing - and dangerous - Homer on a river rafting trip. (S5 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Last Temptation of Homer: Homer falls for his beautiful new colleague Mindy Simmons (guest star Michelle Pfeiffer), who shares his love of doughnuts... (S5 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mercedes and Ste find themselves on a path of self-destruction while the McQueens support Sienna - but drama soon follows...

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Animal Control
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Bulls and Potbellies: US sitcom. Frank and Emily make a breakthrough in their case. Shred bonds with Rick. And Victoria and Patel's father accidentally kiss... (S2 Ep8/9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sonia Dara: The remaining contestants learn that fame is a double-edged sword during an afternoon with fans of the show, before a group shoot where everyone gets covered in mud. (S16 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers have been watching Michael McIntyre's The Wheel, Jamie's 1 Wonders, Top Gear, Guillermo del Toro's Cabinet of Curiosities, and Wild Croc Territory. (S20 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics watch: I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here!, Hollyoaks, Stanley Tucci: Searching for Italy, Queens for the Night, and University Challenge. (S20 Ep10)
